# 🌐 Kallen Mugambi — Portfolio

Welcome to my digital space — a curated collection of the work, ideas, and growth that define my journey as a **developer, designer, and problem-solver**.

This portfolio is more than a showcase.
It’s a reflection of how I think, build, and evolve.

---

## 🚀 About this portfolio

This platform brings together the three pillars of my professional journey:

**Projects • Blogs • Certifications**

Each section tells a different part of the story — not just what I create, but *why* and *how* I create it.

---

