## 🛠 Tech Stack

This portfolio is built using modern tools and practices, including:

* React + TypeScript
* Tailwind CSS
* Component-driven architecture
* Local data modeling (portfolio-friendly structure)
* Cloudinary for media hosting
* Markdown-powered blog engine
* LocalStorage interactions (likes & engagement simulation)

